#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As mentioned above, a reflection occurs when a beam emerges from the same "
"point it was sent in. This can happen in several ways:"
msgstr ""
"यथा उपरि उक्तं, प्रतिबिम्बं तदा भवति यदा किरणः यस्मिन् बिन्दौ प्रेषितः आसीत् तस्मात् एव "
"बिन्दुतः निर्गच्छति ।एतत् अनेकधा भवितुम् अर्हति ।"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"- - - - - - - -         - - - - - - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - O - - -         - - O - O - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"R * * * * - - - -         - - - * - - - -          O - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - O - - -         - - - * - - - -        R - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - * - - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - * - - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -       R * * * * - - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - - O - - -          - - - - - - - -"
msgstr ""
"- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - ओ - - - - - ओ - ओ - - - - - - - - - - - -\n"
"र * * * * - - - - - - - * - - - - ओ - - - - - - - .\n"
"  - - - - वा - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - - - - - * - - - - - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - - - - - * - - - - - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - - - - र * * * * - - - - - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - "
"- - - - - - - - - - - -"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the first example, the beam is deflected downwards by the upper ball, "
"then left by the lower ball, and finally retraces its path to its point of "
"origin. The second example is similar. The third example is a bit anomalous "
"but can be rationalized by realizing the beam never gets a chance to get "
"into the box. Alternatively, the beam can be thought of as being deflected "
"downwards and immediately emerging from the box."
msgstr ""
"प्रथमे उदाहरणे मयूखः ऊर्ध्वकन्दुकेन अधः विक्षिप्तः भवति, ततः अधः कन्दुकेन त्यक्तः भवति, अन्ते "
"च स्वस्य उत्पत्तिबिन्दुपर्यन्तं मार्गं पुनः अनुसृत्य गच्छति द्वितीयं उदाहरणं तथैव । तृतीयं उदाहरणं "
"किञ्चित् विषमम् अस्ति किन्तु किरणः कदापि पेटीयां प्रवेशस्य अवसरं न प्राप्नोति इति अवगत्य "
"तर्कयितुं शक्यते । अथवा मयूखः अधः विक्षिप्तः सद्यः पेटीतः निर्गच्छति इति चिन्तयितुं शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid "A hit occurs when a beam runs straight into a ball:"
msgstr "यदा मयूखः सीधा कन्दुकस्य अन्तः धावति तदा प्रहारः भवति :"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"- - - - - - - -         - - - - - - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - - - - - -          - - - - O - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - - O - - -        H * * * * - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -       H * * * * O - - -          - - - * - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - - O - - -          - - - O - - - -\n"
"H * * * O - - - -         - - - - - - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - - - - - -          - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - - - - - -          - - - - - - - -"
msgstr ""
"- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - ओ - - - .\n"
"  - - - - - - - -         - - - - अहो * * * * - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - - - ह * * * * हे - - - - - - * - - - - .\n"
"  - - - - - - - - - - - - ओ - - - - - - ओ - - - -\n"
"ह * * * ओ - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -\n"
"  - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Be sure to compare the second example of a hit with the first example of a "
"reflection."
msgstr "हिट् इत्यस्य द्वितीयं उदाहरणं प्रतिबिम्बस्य प्रथमेन उदाहरणेन सह अवश्यमेव तुलनां कुर्वन्तु।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface Overview"
msgstr "अन्तरफलक अवलोकन"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Board Description"
msgstr "गेम बोर्ड विवरण"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kblackbox; Game Board</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<स्क्रीनसूचना>&kblackbox; गेम बोर्ड</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kblackbox; Game Board</phrase>"
msgstr "<वाक्यांश>&kblackbox; गेम बोर्ड</phrase> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following types of field are found on the game board:"
msgstr "क्रीडाफलके निम्नलिखितप्रकारस्य क्षेत्रं दृश्यते ।"

#. Tag: interface
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "The big black box in the middle"
msgstr "मध्ये विशालः कृष्णः पेटी"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you must mark the positions you think a ball is in."
msgstr "अत्र भवन्तः कन्दुकं येषु स्थानेषु अस्ति इति मन्यन्ते तानि स्थानानि चिह्नितव्यानि ।"

#. Tag: interface
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lasers around the box"
msgstr "पेटी परितः लेजराः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The lasers are shooting beams of light when switched on. Then, they "
"disappear and are replaced by an information about the interactions of the "
"laser beam with the balls in the black box."
msgstr ""
"लेसराः प्रज्वलिताः सति प्रकाशपुञ्जान् निपातयन्ति । ततः, ते अन्तर्धानं भवन्ति, तेषां स्थाने "
"कृष्णपेटिकायां स्थितैः कन्दुकैः सह लेजर-किरणस्य अन्तरक्रियाणां विषये सूचना भवति ।"

#. Tag: interface
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Balls"
msgstr "कन्दुकाः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>There must be one there!</quote> you think. These mark where you "
"suspect a ball is placed in the black box."
msgstr ""
"<quote>तत्र एकः अवश्यं भवेत्!</quote> इति भवन्तः मन्यन्ते। एते कृष्णपेटिकायां यत्र कन्दुकं "
"स्थापितं इति शङ्कयन्ति तत्र चिह्नयन्ति।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the end of the game, the right and wrong positions of the balls are also "
"marked with <quote>balls</quote>."
msgstr ""
"क्रीडायाः अन्ते कन्दुकस्य सम्यक्-असत्-स्थानयोः अपि <quote>कन्दुक</quote> इति चिह्नं भवति ।"

#. Tag: interface
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid "Markers for \"free position\""
msgstr "\"मुक्तस्थानम्\" इति चिह्नानि ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use them to mark some positions where you are sure there is no ball."
msgstr ""
"भवन्तः तान् उपयुज्य केचन स्थानानि चिह्नितुं शक्नुवन्ति यत्र भवन्तः निश्चिन्ताः सन्ति यत् कन्दुकः "
"नास्ति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Items"
msgstr "मेनू आइटम"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>खेल</guimenu> <guimenuitem>नव</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starts a new game (and abandons the current, if any.)"
msgstr "नूतनं क्रीडां आरभते (वर्तमानं च परित्यजति, यदि अस्ति।)"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>P</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pause</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>P</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>खेल</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>विरामं कुरुत</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pause or continue the current game."
msgstr "वर्तमानक्रीडां विरामं कुर्वन्तु अथवा निरन्तरं कुर्वन्तु।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note that the interaction results are hidden in a paused game."
msgstr "ध्यानं कुर्वन्तु यत् अन्तरक्रियाफलं विरामितक्रीडायां निगूढं भवति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show High Scores</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>खेल</guimenu> <guimenuitem>उच्चाङ्कान् दर्शयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show the high score tables."
msgstr "उच्चाङ्कसारणीः दर्शयन्तु।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Start Tutorial</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>खेल</guimenu> <guimenuitem>पाठ्यक्रमम् आरभत</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Start the tutorial of the game. This is a user friendly way to learn the "
"game rules."
msgstr "क्रीडायाः पाठ्यक्रमं आरभत। एषः क्रीडानियमान् ज्ञातुं उपयोक्तृ-अनुकूलः उपायः अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Sandbox Game</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>क्रीडा</guimenu> <guimenuitem>नवीन सैण्डबॉक्स क्रीडा</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this mode, the solution is displayed at the start of the game. This is "
"useful to understand the game principles."
msgstr ""
"अस्मिन् मोड् मध्ये क्रीडायाः आरम्भे समाधानं प्रदर्शितं भवति । एतत् क्रीडासिद्धान्तान् अवगन्तुं "
"उपयोगी भवति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>प्रश्न</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>खेल</guimenu> <guimenuitem>निवृत्तं</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "This closes the window and quits &kblackbox;."
msgstr "एतेन विण्डो पिधाय &kblackbox;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Solve</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>चल</guimenu> <guimenuitem>समाधानं</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use it to give up a game. It shows you the solution: the right positions of "
"the balls."
msgstr "क्रीडां त्यक्तुं तस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु। समाधानं दर्शयति : कन्दुकानां सम्यक् स्थानानि।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Done!</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>चल</guimenu> <guimenuitem>कृतम्!</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you placed all the balls, choose <guilabel>Done!</guilabel> to "
"terminate the current game, to compute the final score and to display the "
"real positions of the balls."
msgstr ""
"यदा भवान् सर्वाणि कन्दुकानि स्थापितवान् तदा वर्तमानक्रीडायाः समाप्त्यर्थं, अन्तिमस्कोरस्य "
"गणनायै, कन्दुकानाम् वास्तविकस्थानानि प्रदर्शयितुं च <guilabel>Done!</guilabel> इति "
"चिनोतु"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Difficulty</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guisubmenu>कठिनता</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the game difficulty. Harder games have more balls and bigger black "
"box than easier games. You can also play with a custom difficulty level that "
"you can set up in the setting dialog of &kblackbox;."
msgstr ""
"क्रीडायाः कठिनतां चिनोतु। कठिनतरक्रीडासु सुलभक्रीडाणाम् अपेक्षया अधिकाः कन्दुकाः, बृहत्तरं "
"कृष्णपेटी च भवति । भवान् इष्टकठिनतास्तरेन सह अपि क्रीडितुं शक्नोति यत् भवान् &kblackbox; "
"इत्यस्य सेटिङ्ग् संवादे स्थापयितुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Games with 4 balls or less can always be solved with certainty! That is not "
"the case for games with 5 balls or more."
msgstr ""
"४ कन्दुकं वा न्यूनानि वा क्रीडाः सर्वदा निश्चयेन समाधानं कर्तुं शक्यन्ते! ५ कन्दुकं वा अधिकं वा "
"युक्तेषु क्रीडेषु तत् न भवति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kblackbox; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the "
"sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"अतिरिक्तरूपेण &kblackbox; सामान्यं &kde; <guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> तथा "
"<guimenu>सहायता</guimenu> मेनू-वस्तूनाम्, अधिकसूचनार्थं <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">सेटिंग्स् मेन्यू< इत्यस्य विषये विभागान् पठन्तु /"
"ulink> तथा च &kde; मौलिकता।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "बहुधा पृष्टाः प्रश्नाः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play this game?"
msgstr "एतत् क्रीडां कर्तुं कीबोर्डस्य उपयोगं कर्तुं शक्नोमि वा?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. You can use the directional keys to control the cursor, &Enter; to "
"place and remove balls, and &Space; to place <quote>empty</quote> marks."
msgstr ""
"आम्‌। कर्सरं नियन्त्रयितुं भवान् दिशात्मककुञ्जीनां उपयोगं कर्तुं शक्नोति, &Enter; कन्दुकं स्थापयितुं "
"निष्कासयितुं च, &Space; <quote>रिक्त</quote> चिह्नानि स्थापयितुं ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"इदानीं मया क्रीडां त्यक्तव्या, परन्तु अहम् अद्यापि न समाप्तः। अहं मम प्रगतिम् रक्षितुं शक्नोमि "
"वा ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kblackbox; has no save feature at the moment."
msgstr "&kblackbox; अस्मिन् क्षणे save feature नास्ति ।"

